  "title": "F&B Receptionist Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Your main duties are as follows:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Draw up client bookings for tables and ensure that tables are set before clients' arrival</li>\n  <li>Manage the front desk by receiving incoming calls, greeting and attending to customers</li>\n  <li>Inform guests about the availability of tables and direct them to the tables</li>\n  <li>Keep records of guests who visit the restaurant</li>\n  <li>Assist customers with answers to queries, and proffer solutions to issues within your capacity</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with other restaurant staff and the management to ensure that customer complaints are properly attended to in a timely manner</li>\n  <li>Ensure that clients make payment for services before they exit the restaurant</li>\n  <li>Keep clear records of payments received and make detailed notes of balance payments</li>\n  <li>Communicate with other staff, such as dinners, informing them of clients' bookings, needs and complaints.</li>\n  <li>Management of e-reservations across all platforms in the company</li>\n  <li>Adhere to hygiene and safety standards</li>\n  <li>Adhere to company’s standard operating procedures</li>\n  <li>Any other appropriate duties and responsibilities as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 6 days work week, including weekend &amp; PH.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
